oudml/issues/comments/617411877","html_url":"https://github.com/regel/loudml/issues/166#issuecomment-617411877","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/regel/loudml/issues/166","id":617411877,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDYxNzQxMTg3Nw==","user":{"login":"regel","id":355557,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM1NTU1Nw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/355557?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel","html_url":"https://github.com/regel","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2020-04-21T21:01:01Z","updated_at":"2020-04-21T21:01:01Z","author_association":"OWNER","body":"I did it! Setting up this Debian/Ubuntu repo was SO hard but I believe it's done the right way. HTTPS and GPG signatures enabled.\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ curl -s https://deb.loudml.io/install/script.deb.sh | sudo bash\r\nDetected operating system as Ubuntu/bionic.\r\nChecking for curl...\r\nDetected curl...\r\nChecking for gpg...\r\nDetected gpg...\r\nRunning apt-get update... done.\r\nInstalling apt-transport-https... done.\r\nInstalling /etc/apt/sources.list.d/loudml.list...done.\r\nImporting gpg key... done.\r\nRunning apt-get update... done.\r\n\r\nThe repository is setup! You can now install packages.\r\n```\r\n\r\nSo now you can do `apt-get install loudml` on a modern Debian and Ubuntu and it will work.\r\n\r\nOne exception: I could not do Ubuntu Xenial (16.04), python 3.5 is no longer supported in so many pip packages that I have to drop support for Xenial.\r\n\r\nIf you like this work, please give a star to the repo!\r\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/regel/loudml/issues/comments/617411877/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"regel","id":355557,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM1NTU1Nw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/355557?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel","html_url":"https://github.com/regel","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/regel/loudml/issues/comments/657983223","html_url":"https://github.com/regel/loudml/issues/166#issuecomment-657983223","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/regel/loudml/issues/166","id":657983223,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDY1Nzk4MzIyMw==","user":{"login":"regel","id":355557,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM1NTU1Nw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/355557?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel","html_url":"https://github.com/regel","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/regel/gists{/